def spin(a)
	[a[0]] + a[5..6] + a[1..4] + [a[7]]
end

def roll(a)
	a[1..3] + [a[0]] + a[5..7] + [a[4]]
end

while gets
	hash = {}
	a = $_.chomp.split.map{|x| hash[x] ||= hash.size}.sort
	count = 0
	a[1..-1].permutation{|x|
		x.unshift 0
		stack = [x]	
		reached = {}
		ok = true

		while y = stack.pop
			next if reached[y]
			reached[y] = 0
			if hash[y]
				ok = false
				break
			end
			stack << spin(y)
			stack << roll(y)
		end

		hash[x] = 0
		count += 1 if ok
	}
	p count
end

def f(a)
	s = 0
	a[0] -= 1
	if a[0] == 0
		a.shift
		(0..a.size-1).each{|i|
			b = a.dup
			b[i] -= 1
			b.delete_at(i) if b[i] == 0
			s += g(b)
		}
	else
		a[0] -= 1
		s += 720 / a.map{|x| fact(x)}.inject(:*)
		a[0] += 1
		(1..a.size-1).each{|i|
			b = a.dup
			b[i] -= 1
			b.delete_at(i) if b[i] == 0
			s += g(b)
		}
	end
	s
end

def g(a)
	k = a[0]
	s = 720 / a.map{|x| fact(x)}.inject(:*)
	if a == [6]
		s += 2
	elsif a == [3, 3]
		s += 4
	end
	s / 3
end

def fact(x)
	(1..x).inject(1, :*)
end

while gets
	hash = {}
	a = $_.chomp.split.group_by{|x| x}.values.map(&:size)
	p f(a)
end
